Popular Nigerian singer cum disc jockey, DJ Cuppy has taken to a micro blogging site, Twitter to pour out her frustration after the news of Rihanna being pregnant surfaced.
The billionaire daughter took to the platform to lament over being single but the American songstress is pregnant.
The news of Rihanna carrying ASAP Rocky’s child stormed the internet yesterday and fans sent their congratulatory message to the Barbadian star.
Reacting to this, DJ Cuppy stated that Rihanna is now pregnant but she is still single not to talk about getting herself a child
She tweeted, “Rihanna is pregnant and I’m still single”.

Rihanna is pregnant and I’m still single 
— Cuppy (@cuppymusic) January 31, 2022






